      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 21
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3. This specimen features the S54B32 high-revving inline-six, showcasing impeccable compression across all cylinders and a fully overhauled Double VANOS system. The chassis is structurally sound with documented rear subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings throughout. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Every mechanical component, from the individual throttle bodies to the cooling system, has been maintained to an exacting standard. This is a rare, turnkey example with flawless paint and a pristine interior, ready for the most discerning collector.",
